{"tid":2243509,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港版國安法｜美國務院警告金融機構勿與10名受制裁人士交易 包括林鄭月娥","createTime":"2020-10-14T19:43:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T22:42:49.000Z","uid":239336,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"58ceb1ec40c015154f8a4c52f88980f7c32a3526","tid":2243509,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T19:43:46.000Z","msg":"美國國務院周三正式警告國際金融機構勿與因打壓香港民主自治而受制裁的人士交易，否則會面對制裁。<br />\n<br />\n國務院向國會提交報告列出包括特首林鄭月娥在內10名因打壓香港民主而在今年8月被美國財政部制裁的人士，指法例規定國務院須在60天內列出所有曾與他們進行重大交易的金融機構。國務院的報告沒有在制裁名單上添加新名字或點名任何可能受制裁的銀行和金融機構。不過，英美政界人士曾批評滙豐銀行和渣打銀行公開支持實施「港版國安法」。<br />\n<br />\n根據美國的制裁行動，被點名制裁人士在美國的所有資產及權益、直接或間接擁有50%以上股份的公司均會被凍結及必須向財政部海外資產控制辦公室(OFAC)申報，除非得到OFAC發出特別許可，美國人均禁止買賣被制裁人士的資產及權益，亦不可向被制裁人士提供資金、商品和服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201015/L7M7P6NCKVDS7K3TE2B2NNXGZM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0g5ZXsPi3CakcMnuQ5PjxCCxlhbz7A2iPgxIZKMHNgN0X4dgV2cibcNY0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201015%2FL7M7P6NCKVDS7K3TE2B2NNXGZM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0g5ZXsPi3CakcMnuQ5PjxCCxlhbz7A2iPgxIZKMHNgN0X4dgV2cibcNY0&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyiZ4O1D3QR3Td9ugMDSJ%2BOB4%3D&h=41dea54a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201015%2FL7M7P6NCKVDS7K3TE2B2NNXGZM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0g5ZXsPi3CakcMnuQ5PjxCCxlhbz7A2iPgxIZKMHNgN0X4dgV2cibcNY0&h=f4b670dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201015/L7M7P6NCKVDS7K3TE2B2NNXGZM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0g5ZXsPi3CakcMnuQ5PjxCCxlhbz7A2iPgxIZKMHNgN0X4dgV2cibcNY0</a>"},{"pid":"71888427ac3f4c269862576904ad021010ea6494","tid":2243509,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T19:57:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668c085e018b616a9506a4b35195cb5de77666b1","tid":2243509,"uid":279357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T20:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d223b3122f965a74d32815261c47c55f57400e9","tid":2243509,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T20:30:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9c9f67a18bf4d328aecd552ddb91d701e6094f5b","tid":2243509,"uid":86199,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0d223b3122f965a74d32815261c47c55f57400e9","tid":2243509,"uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T20:30:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T20:33:44.000Z","msg":"警告吓遮。 唔使咁緊張"},{"pid":"f15d037e0ce29cd884ea48dd718ec796793edcd3","tid":2243509,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T22:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n提醒11位及金融機構，美帝睇緊，無唔記得左自己帶罪之身"},{"pid":"89ad839fb05e08d9df133da28df38584e11c398d","tid":2243509,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T22:42:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}